title: Packers-Eagles, Baker Mayfield, and 18 game schedule
itunes:title: Packers-Eagles, Baker Mayfield, and 18 game schedule
description:
Colin discusses the Green Bay Packers slowly transitioning from QB Aaron Rodgers and their game tonight against the Philadelphia Eagles, why he feels Cleveland Browns QB Baker Mayfield is getting a raw deal, and why he doesn't want the NFL to have a 18 game season. Guests include Doug Gottlieb, Greg Cosell, Andrew Siciliano, and Bucky Brooks.
